summary:
HR Partner at Trane Technologies - a climate innovator with sustainability embedded into all we do. We are passionate, pioneering people connected by a bold purpose. We uplift others, make an impact, and thrive at work and home. I'm making an impact every day by engaging and supporting our people.

My background in Psychology & Finance enables me to strike an effective balance between big-picture strategic needs and ensuring critical details are addressed. Managing a wide variety of HR projects. HR advisor and expert on Talent Management, People Management, Payroll, Compensation & Benefits, HR Policies, Learning & Development, Performance Management and Organization Development. 

If you are curious to know more - what are you waiting for? Send me a message and join our team!
